text: Lischkeia mahajangaensis is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Eucyclidae. ==Description== The shell grows to a height of 25 mm. ==Distribution== This species occurs in the Indian Ocean off Madagascar. ==References== * Vilvens C. 2002. Description of Lischkeia mahajangaensis n.sp. (Gastropoda: Trochidae: Eucyclinae: Calliotropini) from East Madagascar. Novapex 3(4): 127-131 * Bouchet, P.; Fontaine, B. (2009).
